#FirstImpressionsWithAanam | the @elfcosmetics 16H Camo Cocncealer did NOT start out strong, but clearly, impressed me by the end of it. I used it under my contour as well for a little highlight, and also managed to fix the extra lightness with some loose powder (Fit Me in shade Medium 25). All in all, it lasted with only a few creases till the end of the day. I took my makeup off at about midnight so it was pretty much an ALL day wear! Full points to this one 💯 (only caveat is to be careful while picking the shade on the Nykaa website)

I got my hands on some @r.e.m.beauty and it’s safe to say I have my favourites! ✨

The liquid eyeshadows topped the list for me. They blended out smoothly and were SUPER pigmented, so I would advise you use lesser and build up as needed. I used the shades BRB (soft, natural mauve) and TTYL (second, brown tone)✨

The highlighter (shade: miss mercury) was a close second. It didn’t last as long as I would have liked but went in nice and smooth with a radiating finish ✨

The liner was nice but the tip is different from the usual felt tip liners. So give yourself a use or two to get used to it. It has a glossy finish so keep that in mind as well (I’m a matte finish girl usually) ✨

The mascara for me was most underwhelming. I didn’t find it packing a punch with its promise to add volume as I hoped it would ✨

#GRWAanam #BeautyReviews #REMBeauty

Airbrush Powders were a major risk for a NEW indie brand, when we launched them in April 2022. I loved our product, but I knew it could go either way - either it would prove to be too niche for the general non-pro makeup lovers, or we would be able to bring something exquisite and luxurious to everyday makeup kits. Last night was proof that the result was the latter of the two!

The @wearified IRL Paris Filter Airbrush Powder won the @elleindia Beauty Awards in the category for setting powders / setting sprays with some of the biggest brands in the world nominated in the same category!! This win is SO special to a small brand like ours 💖 Thank you for voting for us, and thank you to the Elle team & Jury that got our products all the way to receive so much love! Use code EBAWIN win to try our IRL Paris Filter Airbrush Powder range at 25% off wearified.in 🛍️ #WearifiedAirbrushPowder #WearifiedIRLParisFilter

Doing up my second home meant having a lot more experience in exactly what I needed from the corners of a house I wanted to make a home. More so as a new mom, I wanted to choose fabrics that were soft and luxurious to the touch. I opted for a @nesterrahomedecor materials for my entire home: from all of our curtains to the upholstery on our bed as well as the sofa and its accent seating.

The brand had such a wide variety of prints to choose from, right from floral to geometric styles. All with colour options, offering so much versatility in the way you’d want to style your home. #NesterraHomeDecor #ChashmaRanjanHome
